Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是您女兒女婿托我捎給您的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是您的信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說牙主動給村民們擔起了聯絡員的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆無論何時都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也試過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是試過一直和佐助在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.75,0:00:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還不是因為同是第七班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起都到了無法分開的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.87,0:01:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我們正執行奪回大名被竊寶物的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據情報所示 盜竊了大名妹妹的黃金像的盜賊 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸路會走森林這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水路船則會到此靠岸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩條路線最有可能遇見他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是需要我們兵分兩路預先設伏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過考慮到戰力均衡問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一人一組 你們三人一組如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為佐助會扯後腿才這麼安排嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 是你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你讓我變弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有差到需要三對一的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把拖後腿的鳴人放到你那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負數相互抵消怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這就是佐助想和我兩人獨處的大膽表白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會變成負值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上沒有增值成分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助因為想要和我單獨相處而變得熱血了 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真夠讓人鬱悶的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我負責停船處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三人負責盯梢森林中的這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦賊人出現 首先通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切勿輕敵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務只是奪回黃金像而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須謹慎執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我遇上賊人也會發出信號的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雷管僅能對天發射一炮雷鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦確認該信號 就必須迅速趕到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要給我小心收好那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 千萬不可擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是盜賊集團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋…重要的寶物可在你這兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 邪湖大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我用心點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物 在那個箱子裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是說…機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓佐助頓失光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也…難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 寶物被…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個傢伙在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該先通知卡卡西老師才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我放開寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的追兵嗎 同伴就那兩人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想發信號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是個純粹的賊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本質早就泥濘不堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以連我的查克拉都能如此腐蝕成形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩人跳河逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以河為中心 分頭搜尋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我把寶物搶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙怎麼處置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為人質也不錯 一起帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西也值得偷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷鳴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知卡卡西用的雷鳴沒放響
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小櫻無法放出雷鳴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻她…被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被粘住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧 很快就能讓你和同伴相見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們交還寶物後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把你們都送到西天去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對忍者來說 手被束縛就毫無作為了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們如此浪費時間 小櫻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 我這就去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嗎呢 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道不顧小櫻的生死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻會得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們這樣什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此也要前去搭救 這才算同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…才不要做個拋棄夥伴的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:12:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不珍惜夥伴的傢伙連廢物都不如
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以跟卡卡西匯合才是最佳選擇 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能提高小櫻的生存幾率
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說什麼生存幾率
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這不是靠我們的努力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了這東西讓小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 住手 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視任務的傢伙也是廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自說自話地搞什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓我…那麼就一隻手來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 距離這麼近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你濺到了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 想尿尿了也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微忍忍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我收起來你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妨礙我了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才干擾到我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把寶物還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單手怎麼結印
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是這種雜兵我們也幹不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不願意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算砍掉我的手我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉這傢伙救回小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡會亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去救小櫻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然敵人已經追到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來在我們找到卡卡西前可能就會被他們發現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好從這傢伙嘴裡套出他們的藏身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後救出小櫻更快捷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那也得看我跟你的默契了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了 要尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 須黑那傢伙還沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是大名妹妹的黃金像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了這東西將我們分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他倆的手分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西就給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要拿我們的同伴交換
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不答應我們的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用我們這雙自由之手幹掉你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不會以為兩名忍者收拾不了你們盜賊集團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎這麼咬牙切齒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且青筋暴露 汗流不止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由了的話 就過來這邊看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他倆的手還連著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好害怕的 抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被識破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆快避開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物…是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑單手是贏不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.多重影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 結印…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是兩個人結印 也依然無法凝練查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是有聯合秘招的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏青哥之術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融掉之後再重新鑄造
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許勉強能過關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少開玩笑了 怎麼連卡卡西老師也拆不開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個首領不是也說過了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過兩三天就會斷裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能跟這傢伙待這麼長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 有感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回是大號了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開國際玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥啦 不已經是共同小便過的夥伴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大跟小是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不珍惜夥伴的傢伙是廢物嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫孩子輕易就做到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務是打倒掠奪村莊的盜賊團伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及救出被俘人質
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的根據地在天然要塞之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有三個堅固的城寨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最棘手的則是首領巴戟非常聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之需要背水一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合 第十班
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 各位
